title: Muhammad Shahbaz Sharif wins PP-158 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz candidate Muhammad Shahbaz Sharif won the Punjab Assembly elections from PP-158 Lahore-XIV by securing 38,642 votes.
According to the unofficial results, issued by the returning officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent Candidate Yousaf Ali who bagged 23,847 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 40.11 percent.
